---
title: Hearty Pork Scotch & Tomato Stew with Cheddar Cheese, Garlic Rice & Parsley
description: If you're planning to stay in with a cosy homecooked dinner, then this stew fits the criteria. Let your slow cooker do the work, transforming tender pork and veggies into a hearty, tomato-based delight. Dig in and enjoy a bowl of pure comfort.
